name: Toyoung
description:
#3 Indonesian Ghost Series

Toyoung aka Tuyul is the ghostly characters of popular Indonesian legend. 

The Tuyul appears as the figure of a child with a bald head, it is believed that Tuyul came from the fetus of a miscarriage or a stillborn child that was filled with evil spirits.

Tuyul has a child's characteristics and loves to play, even in the middle of the night and Tuyul can be employed to steal people’s money. Keep your wallet well because tuyul can steal your money.
